text: :Pages appear in :Category:Country musicians from California This is a list of famous country musicians from California, USA. *Merle Haggard (d. 2016) *Kris Kristofferson (d. 2024), did grow up in CA *Jackson Browne (born 1948), raised in CA *Jon Pardi (born 1985) The following other musicians have had at least one number one song or album on country music charts: Gary Allan. The following other musicians have had at least one "top five" song or album on country music charts: Cam, Devin Dawson, Skip Ewing. ==Related pages== *List of country musicians from Texas ==Sources== *California country musicians
